Subject: [PATCH] drm/i915: Don't overestimate 4:2:0 link symbol clock
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: ddb3d12afa92beb67027e84bbc994b0868446022
